**My option-2 sketch — three substrate slices, dry-run-flagged through v0:**

Slice A — `auto_ship_attempts` ledger (`workflow/auto_ship_ledger.py`):
- Append-only JSON store at `<universe_data>/auto_ship_attempts.jsonl`.
- One row per `validate_ship_request` invocation that returns `validation_result == "passed"` (and later, per actual PR-open). Schema: `{attempt_id, ts, packet_hash, ship_class, decision_summary, would_open_pr, opened_pr_number?, opened_at?, observation_status?, observation_status_at?, rollback_pr_number?, rollback_reason?}`.
